{"tid":1179412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港豬咁撚多年仲係和理非非","createTime":"2019-05-31T05:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T07:37:45.000Z","uid":36134,"like":17,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"589d901b1c9261d064549d0db02dacb62ac1f410","tid":1179412,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"[url]恭喜連登仔退步到成為紅衛兵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1179246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1179246</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n呢d垃圾post都可以過千正評<br />\n仲話理性討論 人地揸住把刀想劈你<br />\n你仲想講道理 講理性？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔通仲要係支共港共面前維持社會安穩繁榮 令佢地覺得逃犯立例都無咩野姐 <br />\n香港都唔會亂既<br />\n你地有無腦架？</span></span><br />\n係呢班人眼中 法國黃背心運動可能係暴動黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本成班法國紅衛兵 又扔氣油彈 又盛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解大家唔可以理性討論姐</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正評個d真係弱智仔黎 咁多年都未識醒<br />\n打緊仗 仲講理性 仲講道理<br />\n而家得立場 人地支共港共企晒隊<br />\n你地唔係以為和理非非可以搞掂對面啊嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係咁既話 我覺得香港真係無救了<br />\n根本呢個時候 唔需要同敵人講道理"},{"pid":"b344c7e0c0d940aab308ef955ff6cf2e72f10c11","tid":1179412,"uid":199352,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:01:08.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢呀 個樓主就係話<br />\n就算佢叫啲人唔好鳩行 （即係做啲其他嘢呀） 都會俾人話五毛<br />\n即係叫人除左行之外仲要做其他呀<br />\n咁都和理非非<br />\n識唔識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafec202ad2788da3d8d14d843911501d01ecb14","tid":1179412,"uid":36134,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJULdab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJULdab.png&h=dedf9a10&s={SIZE}\" />睇到未<br />\n條撚樣根本就係度慫恿人地6月9號唔好上街"},{"pid":"f64059d977800264e15470a2a1d